item.title: HackTheBox - Legacy Writeup
item.author: SH∆FIQ ∆IM∆N
item.description: Enumeration First, let’s do an enumeration with the IP address of this machine. I’m gonna run Nmap [Netwok Mapper] to scan any open ports. I’m gonna run this command 1 nmap -sC -sV -oN nmap/initial 10.10.10.4 Explaining the nmap scan: -sC := scan using nmap default script -sV := scan for version -oN := output in normal format The result: nmap initial scan Again, using Nmap for scanning all ports but nothing new comes up.
